seealso `[SkinWriter]`

This is a C++ interface to `[skin_writer_attr]`.

FUNCTION SkinWriterAttr: (bufferSize: size_t, bufferCount: uint8_t, name: const char *)
	Constructor

	Set the writer attributes.

	INPUT bufferSize
		Size of data buffer.  See `[skin_writer_attr::buffer_size](skin_writer_attr#buffer_size)`
	INPUT bufferCount
		Number of data buffers.  See `[skin_writer_attr::buffer_count](skin_writer_attr#buffer_count)`
	INPUT name
		The name of the writer.  See `[skin_writer_attr::name](skin_writer_attr#name)`

FUNCTION getBufferSize: (): size_t
	Get size of writer data buffer

	This function returns the writer's buffer size.

	OUTPUT
		Returns the `[skin_writer_attr::buffer_size](skin_writer_attr#buffer_size)` attribute.

FUNCTION getBufferCount: (): uint8_t
	Get number of writer data buffers

	This function returns the writer's buffer count.

	OUTPUT
		Returns the `[skin_writer_attr::buffer_count](skin_writer_attr#buffer_count)` attribute.

FUNCTION getName: (): const char *
	Get writer name

	This function returns the writer's name.

	OUTPUT
		Returns the `[skin_writer_attr::name](skin_writer_attr#name)` attribute.
